There is an Educational Administration System database `data/eas_database.db`, which contains the following tables:
- Student(SNo, Name, Sex, Birthday, Major, Scores, Remark)
- Course(CID, CName, Term, CTime, Credit)
- Score(SNo, CID, Score)
